partnerDetails.about:
Rob Bos established Bos Electrical in 1987.  Bos Electrical provides top-of-line electrical services to everyone from the single unit homeowner to the large commercial projects through out Auckland. Each customer is treated with respect and each project is handled in a professional and efficient manner.

As a company that provides top quality electrical services we are proud to be a member of Master Electricians NZ.
Call the team at Bos today to discuss your electrical needs.
